Owner of NoriPro and a professional manga artist.
 She entered the VTuber industry when he produced Inuyama Tamaki. 
Her representative works as a manga artist are "SECRET PRINCESS HIMEGOTO" 
and "Futaba's Family Twins", both of which have been made into anime. 
Her manga business is currently closed.
